&lt;figcaption&gt;Embark on a thrilling journey with the Fantastic Four as they harness their newfound powers to save the world in their first epic adventure!&lt;&#x2F;figcaption&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;My Rating:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; ⭐⭐⭐½ (3.5&#x2F;5 stars)&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Overall, the movie was decent. The storyline and the cast were quite good. What I found less convincing was the attempt to merge the 1930s-1960s era with advanced technology and space travel. This combination didn&#x27;t come across as believable. If retro-futurism was a deliberate choice for the society depicted in the film, it needed more explanation.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
